<solution>
<p><ul><li>4.9003566805664</li></ul></p><p><m>\displaystyle{P}{\left({t}\right)}={1950}{e}^{{{0.11}{t}}}</m></p>
<p>
<m>\displaystyle{3343}={1950}{e}^{{{0.11}{t}}}</m></p>
<p>
<m>\displaystyle\frac{{3343}}{{1950}}={e}^{{{0.11}{t}}}</m></p>
<p>
<m>\displaystyle{\ln{{\left(\frac{{3343}}{{1950}}\right)}}}={0.11}{t}</m></p>
<p>
<m>\displaystyle\frac{{\ln{{\left(\frac{{3343}}{{1950}}\right)}}}}{{0.11}}={t}</m></p>
<p>
<m>\displaystyle{t}={4.9003566805664}</m></p>
</solution>
